Sure Word
---------

“His mercy endures forever.”

I rest in the arms of my Soul Lover.
He holds me safe, like no other.
The world would crush and smother,
But His promises are my sure cover.

For I am sure
There's naught more sure
Than the sure
Word of my Lord

“His mercy endures forever.”

